<%- include ('./partials/header-content') -%>
<main>
  <article>
    <section class="section-lvl1">
      <h2>API Usage</h2>
      <section class="section-lvl2">
        <h3>Get Weather Data</h3>
        <p>To get the weather data for a specific location, go to the route below, replacing <code>&lt;your-latitude&gt</code> with the latitude number for your location and <code>&lt;your-longitude&gt</code> with the longitude number for your location:</p>
        <pre>
          <code class="api-link">https://autumnchris-local-weather-backend.onrender.com/weather?lat=&lt;your-latitude&gt;&lon=&lt;your-longitude&gt;</code>
          <button type="button" class="button copy-button api-weather" title="Copy link to clipboard" aria-label="copy link to clipboard"><span class="copy-icon fa-regular fa-copy"></span></button>
        </pre>
      </section>
      <section class="section-lvl2">
        <h3>Get List of Cities Data</h3>
        <p>To get a list of cities data for a specific search input, go to the route below, replacing <code>&lt;your-city-search-input&gt</code> with the name of the city you are searching for:</p>
        <pre>
          <code class="api-link">https://autumnchris-local-weather-backend.onrender.com/cities?searchInput=&lt;your-city-search-input&gt;</code>
          <button type="button" class="button copy-button api-cities" title="Copy link to clipboard" aria-label="copy link to clipboard"><span class="copy-icon fa-regular fa-copy"></span></button>
        </pre>
      </section>
    </section>
  </article>
</main>